window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Audie Award Nominee, Fantasy, 2013 </b></p> <p>Set in a steampunk version of Victorian England, Lev AC Rosen’s acclaimed debut novel, <i>All Men of Genius,</i> follows the fantastical adventures of Violet Adams. Determined to attend the prestigious Illyria College, Violet gains entrance by masquerading as her twin brother Ashton. But continuing the scheme turns out to be difficult - especially when “Ashton” is faced with blackmail, killer automata, and possible romance with a young duke.</p>"; 
